					"name": "Refresh Assets",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "http://localhost:17932/refresh-assets?force=false",
							"protocol": "http",
							"host": [
								"localhost"
							],
							"port": "17932",
							"path": [
								"refresh-assets"
							],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "force",
									"value": "false",
									"description": "Set to 'true' to force asset reimport (ImportAssetOptions.ForceUpdate)"
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Triggers Unity AssetDatabase refresh. Use force=true for stronger refresh (required after file deletions to prevent CS2001 errors).\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n- `force` (optional): \"true\" to use ImportAssetOptions.ForceUpdate\n\n**Recommended Workflow:**\n1. Make file system changes\n2. Call refresh-assets (force=true for deletions)\n3. Wait for MCP responsiveness\n4. Call compile-and-wait\n\n**Response:**\n- Success: `{\"status\":\"ok\", \"message\":\"Asset database refreshed.\"}`\n- Already running: `{\"status\":\"warning\", \"message\":\"Asset refresh already in progress...\"}`"
					},
					"response": [
						{
